	<Title>
		Ginger for nausea: Does it work?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Ginger for nausea is being studied for possible benefit in treating chemotherapy-induced nausea.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Can taking ginger for nausea reduce or eliminate nausea and vomiting caused by chemotherapy?
	</Question>
